# Test Scenarios

## 1. User Registration
- Validate user can register with valid details.
- Validate error messages for invalid entries.

## 2. Login
- Login with valid credentials.
- Login with invalid credentials.
- Logout functionality.

## 3. Product Catalog
- Browse categories.
- Search products.
- Sort products.

## 4. Product Details
- View product images.
- Add item to wishlist.
- Compare product.

## 5. Cart
- Add to cart.
- Update quantity.
- Remove product.

## 6. Checkout
- Proceed to checkout with valid details.
- Verify order confirmation.

## 7. Account Management
- Edit account details.
- Change password.
- View order history.
